<subSubSection pageId="9" pageNumber="258" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="9.[151,1436,151,464]" pageId="9" pageNumber="258">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,337,151,176]" pageId="9" pageNumber="258">Comments:</emphasis>
<taxonomicName box="[344,595,152,176]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Argopistes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="9" pageNumber="258" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="rubicundus">
<emphasis box="[344,595,152,176]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="258">Argopistes rubicundus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is the most unusual New World species. It can be easily separated from the rest of them by the following character states: body rounded in dorsal view and strongly convex in lateral view, almost hemispherical (
<figureCitation box="[410,546,223,247]" captionStart="FIGURES 20 – 23" captionStartId="8.[151,264,1977,2000]" captionTargetBox="[265,1321,447,1955]" captionTargetId="figure@8.[265,1321,447,1956]" captionTargetPageId="8" captionText="FIGURES 20 – 23. Argopistes rubicundus Blake. 20 dorsal habitus; 21 lateral habitus; 22 head, frontal view; 23 aedeagus, ventral, lateral and dorsal views." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/216668/files/figure.png" pageId="9" pageNumber="258">Figs 20, 21</figureCitation>
); aedeagus strongly arched in lateral view (
<figureCitation box="[1054,1140,223,247]" captionStart="FIGURES 20 – 23" captionStartId="8.[151,264,1977,2000]" captionTargetBox="[265,1321,447,1955]" captionTargetId="figure@8.[265,1321,447,1956]" captionTargetPageId="8" captionText="FIGURES 20 – 23. Argopistes rubicundus Blake. 20 dorsal habitus; 21 lateral habitus; 22 head, frontal view; 23 aedeagus, ventral, lateral and dorsal views." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/216668/files/figure.png" pageId="9" pageNumber="258">
Fig. 
<number box="[1109,1140,223,247]" pageId="9" pageNumber="258" value="23.0">23</number>
</figureCitation>
); spermathecal receptacle elongate, nearly parallel-sided (
<figureCitation box="[504,589,260,284]" captionStart="FIGURES 24 – 26" captionStartId="9.[151,264,1146,1169]" captionTargetBox="[265,1320,520,1109]" captionTargetId="figure@9.[265,1321,519,1124]" captionTargetPageId="9" captionText="FIGURES 24 – 26. Argopistes rubicundus Blake. 24 spermatheca; 25 vaginal palpi; 26 tignum." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/216669/files/figure.png" pageId="9" pageNumber="258">
Fig. 
<number box="[557,589,260,284]" pageId="9" pageNumber="258" value="24.0">24</number>
</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
